Introduction

YOUNITE is an eight-member boy group under Brand New Music. As nine, the group debuted on April 20, 2022, with 1st EP Album "YOUNI-BIRTH".

The members are Eunho, Eunsang, Steve, Hyungseok, Woono, DEY, Kyungmun, and Sion.

The group name "YOUNITE" represents the idea that “YOU and I: we are connected.”

On July 1st, 2024 Brand New Music announced that member Hyunseung decided to leave YOUNITE due to personal reasons after taking a break from activities since June 12.
